      "layout": "The page adheres to a max-width centered content model, creating visual stability. The header floats at the top, consistent across different content. The hero section is full-bleed 'Deep Teal' with a prominent centered headline and descriptive text, followed by the primary CTA. Content sections follow a vertical rhythm with generous spacing. Information is presented in clear, distinct blocks, often utilizing a multi-column grid for features or data like the 'Risk Indicator' modules. The layout is spacious with strong visual separation between content blocks.",
